# Webhooks Service

FastAPI service that receives Slack messages, applies filtering logic, and persists qualifying messages to database.

## Purpose

Inbound webhook endpoint for Slack integration. Messages are evaluated against configurable filters. Approved messages are stored for further processing.

## Structure

```
app/
├── controllers/    # API routes
├── services/       # Business logic
├── schemas/        # Data models
└── core/          # Configuration
```

## Setup

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Docker

```bash
docker build -t webhooks .
docker run -p 8000:8000 webhooks
```
